Worldwide datasets

jhu = jhu_data()
DT::datatable(jhu[sample(1:nrow(jhu),500),] %>%
              dplyr::arrange(CountryRegion, date),
              extensions = 'Scroller', options = list(scrollX=TRUE))

European datasets

eucov = eu_data_cache_data()
DT::datatable(eucov[sample(1:nrow(eucov),500),] %>%
